{
  "stem": "7458.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "But without hygiene, without food, it was just a nightmare.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "Now, to go out to beg for food was very dangerous.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "We had one interesting incident one summery night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 100,
      "text": "It was late summer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 101,
      "text": "The corn-- well, there in Poland, wheat they called corn.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 102,
      "text": "And so the wheat was fairly high.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 103,
      "text": "It was already brownish-yellow, almost ready to be cut, and very high.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 104,
      "text": "And we went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 105,
      "text": "We would take turns going out begging for food.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 106,
      "text": "And that night, Ruvak, the older of the two brothers, and I went off maybe five miles away to a village to go from door to door to ask if they would give us some bread, some bacon, whatever.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 107,
      "text": "And we had collected some food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 108,
      "text": "It was a very bright night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 109,
      "text": "There were-- there was a full moon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 110,
      "text": "And we were walking on a path not far from the village, when suddenly from nowhere a group of Polish young men armed with pistols and rifles showed up and faced us and asked us to identify ourselves.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 111,
      "text": "And of course, they were out to look for Jews and kill them off.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 112,
      "text": "They were helping the Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 113,
      "text": "And we-- the minute we realized who they were, we didn't answer, and we dropped to the ground.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 114,
      "text": "We were on a narrow path and there was wheat on both sides.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 115,
      "text": "So I dropped on one side in the wheat and Ruvak dropped on the other side, and we started crawling on our hands and knees.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 116,
      "text": "And they were firing away from rifles and pistols at us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 117,
      "text": "And I crawled as far as I could.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 118,
      "text": "And then I got up, and I ran.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 119,
      "text": "And I ran the whole five miles and came back into the forest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 120,
      "text": "By the way, we developed a tremendous sense of directions.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
